{"tid":1079864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=？ 九巴車長駕駛不夠專注　令男子從14米天橋墮下至半癱　入獄15月","createTime":"2019-03-27T08:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T08:50:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54ef902535387700f88705644090f450c03b113d","tid":1079864,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:03:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2601335/org/42daf7aba668af2e10d9cd558e5a6cc9.jpg/sO6voQckIeKKHd9EIVP5nVXgdUVniMNxKgQKnCoECpw?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2601335%2Forg%2F42daf7aba668af2e10d9cd558e5a6cc9.jpg%2FsO6voQckIeKKHd9EIVP5nVXgdUVniMNxKgQKnCoECpw%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=32bcd54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴女通宵車長前年深夜駕駛至荃灣路時，遇上處理中的交通意外現場仍沒有減速，令一名站在路旁的司機被撞至墮下14米天橋，從此半身癱瘓，女司機早前被裁定危駕罪成，案件今（27日）於區域法院判刑，法官指被告非短暫時間不專心，指案情嚴重，判被告入獄15月及停牌3年，並須自費進修駕駛改進課程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/311000/九巴女車長駕駛不夠專注-令男子從14米天橋墮下至半癱-入獄15月\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F311000%2F%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%A5%B3%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A0%E5%B0%88%E6%B3%A8-%E4%BB%A4%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%BE%9E14%E7%B1%B3%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B%E8%87%B3%E5%8D%8A%E7%99%B1-%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%8415%E6%9C%88&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=016d7d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/311000/九巴女車長駕駛不夠專注-令男子從14米天橋墮下至半癱-入獄15月</a>"},{"pid":"6ef3e13f33e82c9139ed056a0f59ff39f878634a","tid":1079864,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:04:47.000Z","msg":"返工=Double Jail<br />\n<br />\n1st  working jail<br />\n<br />\n2nd 赤柱jail"},{"pid":"ca67eb451ae17755c23a5c52aef6006ae8bf2332","tid":1079864,"uid":143667,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"笑死，半身癱瘓判得年半，扣埋假一年出返嚟<br /